# propertyName

**Instance Property**

The name of the CSS property associated with the transition.

## Declaration

```swift
readonly attribute DOMString propertyName;
```

## Accessing Properties

- **elapsedTime**: The duration of the transition, in seconds, since this event was sent. This value is not affected by the value of the CSS `transition-delay` property.

- **Safari CSS Visual Effects Guide**
